abstract: Auto Racing Roundup; Kurt Busch wins AAA 400 at Dover International Speedway in Delaware, moving to fourth in Sprint Cup standings; other racing news noted.
snippet: Kurt Busch held off Jimmie Johnson and Carl Edwards to move from ninth to fourth in the points race.
lead_paragraph: Kurt Busch held off Jimmie Johnson and Carl Edwards to move from ninth to fourth in the points race.

headline.main: Kurt Busch Hangs on at Dover, Moving Up in the Chase Standings
headline.print_headline: At Dover, Kurt Busch Hangs On And Moves Up in Chase Standings
headline.seo: Kurt Busch Wins at Dover and Moves Up in Chase Standings
